{"tid":1244041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6.21 切忌恐慌走避","createTime":"2019-06-19T17:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T17:53:31.000Z","uid":150625,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"832946cef6d4ad9cb12017aac3c8016dd71886b1","tid":1244041,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:14:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n冇錯! 近距離催淚胡椒膠彈好惡頂好痛甚至有機會傷亡<br />\n但係香港已經到左我地唔能夠逃避既狀態<br />\n唔理係和理派定勇武派<br />\n大家做左咁多身心準備有埋至低限度裝備<br />\n切忌因為冒警暴徙射催淚胡椒膠彈就恐慌走避<br />\n輸勢其次 最重要係好可能唔小心變成人踩人傷害到你自己同其他人<br />\n要記住我地大家好多人一齊! 有準備! 唔好驚! <br />\n展現堅韌既勇氣 切忌恐慌走避!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"f85191ceebbf9bdc2c3badb2dca1c2c58400c59d","tid":1244041,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7206b1ff2f606459b4be6a6b40252c7c84acc1f","tid":1244041,"uid":254729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:16:49.000Z","msg":"621圍立法會定禮賓府<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243737</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2edcd5456453a53375c141dd77ac3fd119603825","tid":1244041,"uid":710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffdcc956129c59d1dabe21f61d027c28381a98f7","tid":1244041,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:21:16.000Z","msg":"唔好亂衝比啲狗有籍口升級武力!"},{"pid":"a9a6f65a2705eefc20c35074a0d1da73027cf8cf","tid":1244041,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB